Terminate Tomcat server on windows
Step 1: Check all open ports
        netstat -aon | find /i “listening”
Step 2: Filter all server by port
        netstat -aon |find /i “listening” |find “8080”
Step 3: Kill the server using pid
        taskkill /F /PID 189

Install Java on Ubuntu
Step 1: > apt-get install openjdk-11-jre openjdk-11-jdk
Step 2: > java --version


Install Tomcat on Ubuntu
Step 1 > apt-get install tomcat2

Start tomcat server
cd /etc/init.d
systemctl status apache2
systemctl start apache2
systemctl stop apache2
systemctl restart apache2
